:: Public Holidays
: New Year's Day
"中華民國開國紀念日 / 元旦"     public on January 1
: Lunar New Year's Eve
"農曆除夕"                    public on February 4
: Spring festival
"春節"                       public on February 5 - 8
: Peace Memorial Day
"228和平紀念日"               public on February 28 - March 1
: The Combined Holidays of Women's Day and Children's Day
"婦女節、兒童節合倂"            public on April 4
: Tomb Sweeping Day
"淸明節"                      public on April 5
: Dragon Boat Festival
"端午節"                      public on June 7
: Mid-Autumn Festival       
"中秋節"                      public on September 13
: National Day/Double Tenth Day
"國慶日 / 雙十節"             public on October 10

